ssets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8789b871e015e87be194bd9bf6c9e95680b6f45","tid":350380,"uid":64044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T19:17:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>愛係你願意犧牲自己付出所有 好易無咗自己緊張對方多過自己 對方變成點你都接受 可以好痛苦<br />\n鐘意係覺得好甜蜜 得到係當下嘅快樂但唔長久<br />\n好感 多數係剛認識 比性格外貌吸引覺得對方係可取嘅對象<br />\n好似係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁我應該成世都只係試過不斷鐘意人，未試過真正愛一個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個個都話愛好痛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />算啦唔識愛人都係好事黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ef04d41230dec718578dfb129987b0975efa1a1","tid":350380,"uid":64044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T19:17:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果佢成身人癱左...<br />\n鐘意=照顧到佢自己頂唔順<br />\n愛= 俾佢安樂死 放佢係心裏最重要既位置<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我愛我屋企人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4da4c6b1d3db383b6ac5ba272f2948920ed6905","tid":350380,"uid":83016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T21:12:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果佢成身人癱左...<br />\n鐘意=照顧到佢自己頂唔順<br />\n愛= 俾佢安樂死 放佢係心裏最重要既位置<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我愛我屋企人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nthats why 啲人話越愛一個人就越唔想同對方一齊 因為會企喺對方嘅立場 做對對方最好嘅選擇"},{"pid":"216e899e271af86e419998bff16403a63d2f0383","tid":350380,"uid":33476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T01:07:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌<img src=\"/as